name: For My First (Geome) Trick
description: Feast your eyes on this soothing spectacle that just happens to be my first project I ever made in Grasshopper 3D (ever ever ever), a feat unto itself. Curves subtly expand and contract into a scintillating tapestry of geometric goodness, washing you away into mathematical meditation. This particular eye massage is a parametric paradise of perfect proportion.  Hit me up if you want it in a specific color or in its original red tinge.  http://lynkfire.com/thecryptory .
